{
  "stem": "8.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And, so this is the kind of model my mother was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Not so much the nurturing and understanding person, but the one that always stood up, that always was there when there was a problem, and she was very courageous and strong.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "My father was somewhat different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "My father was a milder person, more gentle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And, I remember when my mother and father had an argument about how much to charge in the restaurant, my father always said just as much as we need and a little bit after that, but not more than that because we cannot take advantage of people.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, my mother, who came from a business family, who always helped her father, could not understand that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How can you lead a business like that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How can-- so indeed, we didn't do so well financially and often had to have our grandparents help to make it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember my parents often worrying, especially the later years, how they're going to pay the rent.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later, my family opened another restaurant in a resort place not far from Miskolc.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, my father used, used to carry the food out from Miskolc to Tapolca, was the name of this place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't know how to ride the bike.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he learned at age 46 or something how to ride the bike and carry the merchandise out there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if I answered most of the things that I might want to talk about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was from 1928, when I was born, to about 1942 or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At 1942, when I finished the middle school, I could not go on to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would not take any Jews into the non-Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- and they closed the only Jewish higher education, which was a teacher's training seminar.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
